Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:10.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,It's Megumu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:12.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:15.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you tell him, Ruri-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:18.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be better if \Nwe didn't let this drag out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:22.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu, why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:26.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,My sisters came and are staying nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:29.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,so they snuck into our place and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:32.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,switched all my clothes for girls clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:33.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:37.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sorry for worrying you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:53.37,Kanojo_Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}If {\c&H53AC43&}Her {\c&H085DF0&}Flag {\c&HD2C345&}Breaks
