Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:19.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,So you agreed to be brother and sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:24.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm now Souta-oniichan's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:26.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Little sisters are nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:30.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:33.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:37.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bad thing to care more about \Nlittle sisters than older ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:41.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You like little sisters better?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okiku-nee, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanted a little sister that badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,why not just be with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,your little android sister right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not you, too, Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make things worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:03.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter how \Nhappy I am to have a brother if
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to hurt his \Nolder sister in the process...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,If you're my brother's little sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,then you're his older sister's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I need to be \Nthe older sister here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,and recognize you as the little \Nsister of my younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hug, hug, hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd like to take Kurumiko back with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:22.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,us to Hatagaya Academy, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:25.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Little Souta's asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Do something for us, Little Mimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not taking no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:35.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,When did you start spoiling him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Please, President...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:44.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,She's the chairwoman's granddaughter, \Nso she's always pulling a lot of stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,but that sometimes comes in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for introducing myself so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:54.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,What? This doesn't taste like anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:03.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we'll have to \Nuse "give and take" here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:07.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... As compensation, how about \Nduring tomorrow's free period,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Souta goes on a date with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,A-A date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're just making light of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:18.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,A date with Seiteikouji \NMimori doesn't come cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you'll just have \Nto buy her a juice box.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,A date with me's worth less than a juice box?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,A date'll be fine. I want the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I've kind of wanted some \Ngood summer memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's settled, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:37.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,If you fall in love with me, \NHatate, it's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,You know it's not like I'm really
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,excited because it's our first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:01.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,There's a beautiful stream \Ndeep in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.22,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of nice to be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:21.30,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,with a girl whose flag I \Ncan't get in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm boring, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:27.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,No normal guy would want
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,to go on a date with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:40.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you spend time with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:44.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can for Kurumiko-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really dislike you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,You're kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:54.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a loud person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm not really that girly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:00.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't stop being who I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,nor do I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:06.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm Seiteikouji Mimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:15.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,you're living earnestly, unlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:19.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You might cause a lot of ruckus,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but you're just enjoying life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You really stand out to me, \Nsince I've given up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.16,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Mimori,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.35,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm envious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.76,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:38.79,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, everyone thinks you're \Nfar better than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.28,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,You might always be causing trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:45.80,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,but that means you're living life to the \Nfullest, standing out to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:50.34,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you should stay the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.31,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.07,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:04.32,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,if I'm really living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:13.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're at the center of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's something to be proud of,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:18.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm sure everyone loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be alive, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone alive must become happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate-kun, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:39.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.98,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a flag, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:52.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:57.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:01.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... You can depend on me. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,If everyone turns against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:07.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there for you, Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I called you by your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:14.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:15.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun. Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of Kurumiko-kun, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:42.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone, get on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in line and don't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:52.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to come, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:54.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate-kun isn't the one at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:02.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sad I'll have to be away from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:05.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,but our hearts will be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:07.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:10.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:13.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we were just able to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:17.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,and become brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:19.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:32.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, the beach was fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:33.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:38.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go again with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,If Souta's going, I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:41.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:42.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Okiku,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:46.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, if everyone's going, \NI guess I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:52.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can go if we \Ndon't have to go to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:54.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kurumiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:04.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,A nice girl brought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:14.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Daimyouzamurai Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I just altered the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,school's data, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You're useless when it matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:36.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:37.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,How mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:42.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So why are the student council \Npresident and Granny here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:46.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,That's because we're going to \Nlive here at Quest Dorm, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,We already completed the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:51.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to get me to\Nowe you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:53.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't like what was \Nhappening, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:58.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumiko-chan, the \Nstudent council president,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:07.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, and Mei! All four \Nof you are moving in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:12.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I have no plans on getting \Nfriendly with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like it if a nice girl
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:19.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,like you was around...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then let's sleep together tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:34.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to sleep by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:38.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Just ask Hatate Souta for—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Just today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't look it, but she was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:05.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Daimyouzamurai... You—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:06.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:10.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You can see flags, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but my power is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:14.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,artificial and limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,However, you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to alter flags...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:24.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You were given that power by the sacraments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrament?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It's something which a human would
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:33.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,normally never be able to possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:36.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,A power which allows one \Nto alter fate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel Boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:40.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It travels all water in existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:47.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,a boat of fate capable of \Ncontrolling all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:51.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You have a power on that level, Hatate Souta,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,and what do you wish to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:00.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'd like to rid \Nmyself of this death flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,First?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The second is a request from Sakura,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:11.06,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.43,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,And in exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.56,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,you must learn the ultimate \Ntruth of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate truth of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:21.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Those who seek will find happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,for you learn the most when you \Nrealize how little you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:37.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Phase shift, clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:40.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Spacial link, clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Gate release.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shall show you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,part of the truth of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't go anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:55.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait. Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:00.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the Hatagaya \NAcademy building, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:02.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:08.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:10.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:15.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Another first year trying to \Ndo something to Kikuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rin-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:19.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I never said you could call me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:24.06,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we mistook you for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the girls in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This world...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:45.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,In order to put it into \Nsomething you'd understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,We're on an Earth from a parallel universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Parallel universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of the Seven \NVirtues watches the worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:55.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of the Seven Virtues?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:59.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Right now we're currently watching
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:03.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,the Sacraments and you, \NHatate Souta, the closest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:06.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It is my job to figure out if
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:08.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,you will bring harm to the worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:10.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:16.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Your power is far greater than you realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:29.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:14.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the Premium Ambriel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.20,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:32.08,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:37.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:40.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to be alone, \Nthen I might as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You might think it's
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:50.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,better to die here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:52.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I still want you to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You will meet people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,People who will be happy you lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,met everyone at Quest Dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:10.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miyuki-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:24.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd hear about Quest Dorm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:25.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:28.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little before the Second World War,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:32.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,my great grandfather went \Nmissing underground there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Under Quest Dorm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, who's you great grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think his name was Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:50.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to mention it, \Nbut my name is Hatate Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:54.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:18:00.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reason to live now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:08.09,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's the main character flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:11.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Your words have given me power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,and I just like you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:22.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world you started in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:23.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:30.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,That world will revolve \Naround Miyuki MacKenzie, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:35.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, as the main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You have an enormous power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:40.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,capable of altering they \Nvery core of a world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:43.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,And using that power, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:51.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine, after I rest a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:56.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:01.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got closer to the ultimate \Ntruth of the world, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:04.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:07.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Is the activated death flag in \Nyou making you say all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:08.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he's going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.45,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,This is death...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:21.05,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,This is fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.31,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The truth behind the power to change flags.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:28.06,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You must bear all the fate in the world by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.66,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:31.44,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.79,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Afraid! Afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:36.06,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But he's born this burden for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,This person will save
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.57,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,the Council of the Seven Virtues, and the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Mother! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:47.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:01.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I've only delayed its activation temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:06.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You're so weak, so naïve, but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:10.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud I saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:15.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know your warmth \Ncould be so endearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The Sacraments!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:27.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:30.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you doing all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:35.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,The apostles of the seven virtues \Nknow too many things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,that he can't be allowed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:46.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,He will find the ultimate truth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:48.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,of the world on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:00.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The next thing I knew I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.83,complete_21:06,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:09.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The conquest completed flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:14.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:16.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Mei, can you see flags?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Council of the Seven Virtues?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:21.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Flags? The Council of the Seven Virtues?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:24.51,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Her memory's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:26.71,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:12.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:14.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're half-Japanese, right, Miyuki-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:16.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:18.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure why you said \N"it turns out," but whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:19.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,There's a big difference between you and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:21.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,even though we're both half-Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:25.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your boobs will get bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:26.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about our height!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:31.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kids grow fast, so I'm sure you'll look \Ndifferent by the start of summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's the "I'm totally \Nnot getting bigger" flag!
